    "Fig. 7 Super-topics found by applying community detection on network of small topics Hierarchical Topic DetectionThree probabilistic graphical topic models, namely HLDA [29], PAM [45], and HPA 15 [55] serve as our hierarchical baselines.HLDA can produce topics at three levels, which are probability distributions over vocabulary terms, and thus, they are compatible with our evaluation metrics without any modifications."
